### Privacy Policy for Ploto - AI Writer

**Last Updated:** Sunday, 08 September 2024

At Ploto - AI Writer, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

### 1. Information We Collect
We collect the following information when you use Ploto - AI Writer:

- **Prompts and Generated Text**: We store the prompts you enter, the settings you use, and the generated text. This data is stored to enable account history and allow access to past results on any device where you use the same account.
  
- **Usage Data**: We may collect non-identifiable data such as app usage statistics to improve our services.

### 2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected data for the following purposes:

- **Account History**: To allow you to access your generated text and prompts across devices.
- **App Improvement**: To analyze usage trends and improve app functionality.

### 3. Data Storage and Security
- We store your prompts, generated text, and related settings securely in our database. This data is tied to your account for easy access across devices.
- We do **not** store or use the data you enter for AI model training purposes.
- We take security seriously and implement appropriate measures to protect your data.

### 4. In-App Purchases and Subscriptions
Ploto - AI Writer includes in-app purchases and subscriptions. You can test the app with free prompts, but a subscription is required to generate additional text.

### 5. Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services, such as payment processors, that adhere to their own privacy policies.

### 6. Data Retention
We retain your data (prompts, generated text, settings) as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, your data will be permanently removed.

### 7. Your Rights
You have the right to access, modify, or delete your account information. Please contact us for assistance.

### 8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the app.

If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at moorphism@gmail.com

---

By using Ploto - AI Writer, you agree to this Privacy Policy.
